  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Inspired by the monolith from 2001. A single, impossibly pure tone with maximum partials in perfect alignment. No formant coloring, no vibrato, no modulation — just the raw harmonic series at total synchrony. The sound is so clean it feels alien. It does not invite interaction. It transmits.",
